define
  # Attributes
  attribute name value string;
  attribute location value string;
  attribute ip value string;
  attribute zone value integer;
  attribute size value integer;
  attribute rack_number value integer;
  attribute type_id value integer;
  attribute machine_type value string;
  attribute ram value integer;
  attribute disk value integer;
  attribute cpu value integer;
  attribute start_time value integer;
  attribute pid value integer;
  attribute port_number value integer;

  # Entities
  entity data_center,
    owns name @key,
    owns location,
    plays dc_contains:data_center;

  entity router,
    owns name @key,
    owns zone,
    plays dc_contains:contained_equipment,
    plays routes:routing_device;

  entity egress,
    owns name @key,
    plays dc_contains:contained_equipment,
    plays routes:routing_device;

  entity interface,
    owns ip @key,
    plays routes:routed_interface,
    plays exposes:exposing_interface,
    plays connects:interface;

  entity network,
    owns ip @key,
    owns size,
    owns zone,
    plays routes:routing_device;

  entity network_zone,
    owns ip @key,
    owns size,
    owns zone,
    plays routes:routing_device;

  entity rack,
    owns name @key,
    owns zone,
    owns rack_number,
    plays dc_contains:contained_equipment,
    plays holds:containing_rack;

  entity switch,
    owns ip @key,
    owns rack_number,
    plays holds:held_equipment,
    plays routes:routing_device;

  entity machine_type_spec,
    owns type_id @key,
    owns machine_type,
    owns name,
    owns ram,
    owns disk,
    owns cpu,
    plays typed_as:spec;

  entity machine,
    owns name @key,
    plays holds:held_equipment,
    plays runs:host_machine,
    plays routes:routing_device,
    plays typed_as:machine;

  entity software,
    owns name @key,
    plays has_version:versioned_software,
    plays depends_on:dependent,
    plays depends_on:dependency,
    plays instance_of:template;

  entity os,
    owns name,
    owns start_time,
    plays runs:running_process,
    plays instance_of:running_instance;

  entity service,
    owns name,
    owns start_time,
    owns pid,
    plays runs:running_process,
    plays listens:listening_process,
    plays depends_on:dependent,
    plays depends_on:dependency,
    plays instance_of:running_instance,
    plays instance_of:template;

  entity application,
    owns name,
    owns start_time,
    owns pid,
    plays runs:running_process,
    plays listens:listening_process,
    plays depends_on:dependent,
    plays depends_on:dependency,
    plays instance_of:running_instance,
    plays instance_of:template;

  entity version,
    owns name,
    plays has_version:release_version,
    plays instance_of:template,
    plays depends_on:dependency,
    plays previous:newer_version,
    plays previous:older_version;

  entity process,
    owns name,
    owns start_time,
    owns pid,
    plays runs:running_process,
    plays listens:listening_process,
    plays depends_on:dependent,
    plays depends_on:dependency,
    plays instance_of:running_instance;

  entity port,
    owns port_number @key,
    plays exposes:exposed_port,
    plays listens:listened_port;

  # Relations
  relation dc_contains,
    relates data_center,
    relates contained_equipment;

  relation routes,
    relates routing_device,
    relates routed_interface;

  relation exposes,
    relates exposing_interface,
    relates exposed_port;

  relation connects,
    relates interface;

  relation holds,
    relates containing_rack,
    relates held_equipment;

  relation runs,
    relates host_machine,
    relates running_process;

  relation typed_as,
    relates machine,
    relates spec;

  relation has_version,
    relates versioned_software,
    relates release_version;

  relation depends_on,
    relates dependent,
    relates dependency;

  relation instance_of,
    relates running_instance,
    relates template;

  relation listens,
    relates listening_process,
    relates listened_port;

  relation previous,
    relates newer_version,
    relates older_version;

schema:
define
  attribute name value string;
  attribute created_at value datetime;
  attribute stream_id value string;
  attribute description value string;
  attribute url value string;
  attribute followers value integer;
  attribute total_view_count value integer;
  attribute team_id value string;

  entity stream,
    owns name @key,
    owns created_at,
    owns stream_id,
    owns description,
    owns url,
    owns followers,
    owns total_view_count,
    plays game_play:streaming_channel,
    plays language_usage:channel,
    plays moderation:moderated_channel,
    plays moderation:moderating_channel,
    plays chat_activity:chatting_channel,
    plays chat_activity:channel_with_chatters,
    plays team_membership:member_stream,
    plays vip_status:vip_channel,
    plays vip_status:channel_with_vips;

  entity game,
    owns name @key,
    plays game_play:played_game;

  entity language,
    owns name @key,
    plays language_usage:used_language;

  entity user,
    owns name @key,
    owns followers,
    plays chat_activity:chatting_user,
    plays chat_activity:user_with_chatters,
    plays moderation:moderated_user,
    plays moderation:moderating_user,
    plays vip_status:vip_user;

  entity team,
    owns created_at,
    owns name,
    owns team_id @key,
    owns followers,
    plays team_membership:organization;

  relation game_play,
    relates streaming_channel,
    relates played_game;

  relation language_usage,
    relates channel,
    relates used_language;

  relation moderation,
    relates moderating_channel,
    relates moderated_channel,
    relates moderating_user,
    relates moderated_user;

  relation chat_activity,
    relates chatting_channel,
    relates channel_with_chatters,
    relates chatting_user,
    relates user_with_chatters;

  relation team_membership,
    relates member_stream,
    relates organization;

  relation vip_status,
    relates vip_channel,
    relates channel_with_vips,
    relates vip_user;
